Product description

Peace of mind, peace of mind, and harmony

Fesasn has a team of professionals who have been focusing on the design and manufacture of transformers for many years, constantly improving the technology to meet the needs of consumers. Our team has developed a new and upgraded design that completely solves the problem of noise and heat generated during use, and the AC24V stable output makes your visual doorbell work perfectly. With this doorbell adapter, you can charge the doorbell continuously without worrying about the doorbell product working interruption, which makes it an excellent special transformer for Ring doorbells. You don't need to remove the battery inside the doorbell, just connect this transformer and charge the doorbell at any time, which is what we want it to do for you

24V power adapter compatible with：24V US power cables for your popular smart thermostats (Nest 1/2nd, Ecobee, Honeywell, Sensi) and doorbells (Ring Video Doorbell, Ring Video Doorbell 2 and Ring Video Doorbell Pro, Nest Skybell, etc.) and other devices that require a constant AC 24 volt power supply, enabling you to safely charge your devices


Long enough cable to facilitate the arrangement and installation of doorbells or thermostats


The shell is made of PC+ABS material, which is fire-resistant and anti drop, ensuring safe and reliable use


Adopting pure copper wire design, sufficient power, low heat generation, and good stability


For doorbells

1.Keep adapter unplugged. 2.Install wires from 24 volt adapter into the terminals for your doorbell unit (Simply attach the two exposed copper wires to the doorbell and tighten the screws, regardless of positive or negative polarity) 3.Plug adapter into outlet. 4.Power up and verify your doorbell is receiving necessary power using the accompanying application.


For thermostats

1.Cut off the power of circuit breaker. 2.Install the wire from your 24 volt adapter to the “C” terminal and the other wire to the “RC” terminal. You need to use included jumper and connect from “RH” to “RC” terminals，if HVAC system has a cooling. 3.Plug the power adapter into the socket and turn on the power of the circuit breaker. Install the panel on the thermostat.


Widely compatible

Compatible with Ring Video Doorbell Compatible with Ring Video Doorbell 2 Compatible with Skybell Doorbell Compatible with Honeywell Smart Wifi Thermostat Compatible with Nest Thermostat Compatible with Ecobee Thermostat Compatible with Sensi Thermostat
